rova, A.E., Creating of the Permanent Space Patrol of Ionizing Solar Radiation (2002) Innovative Telescopes and Instrumentation for Solar Astrophysics, 4853, pp. 600-611. , Keil, S. L. and Avakyan, S. V., Eds., Proc. SPIE; Avakyan, S.V., Baranova, L.A., Kuvaldin, E.V., Leonov, N.B., Savinov, E.P., Savuyshkin, A.V., Voronin, N.A., Nikolenko, A.D., Space Solar Patrol Data and the Weather-Climate Changes, Including the Global Warming (2009) Proc. 9th Int. Symp. Measurement Technology and Intelligent Instruments, pp. 22-43. , St. Petersburg, Russia: ISTC Special Session; Avakyan, S.V., Baranova, L.A., Leonov, N.B., Savinov, E.P., Voronin, N.A., Space Solar Patrol Data and Changes in Weather and Climate, Including Global Warming (2010) Measur. Sci. Technol., 21 (8), p. 15; Avakyan, S.V., Bolgartseva, M.P., Efremov, A.I., Krinberg, I.A., Kulakov, A.P., Petrov, V.S., Podmoshenskii, A.L., Shaulin, Y.N., Fluxes of Electrons During a Magnetic Storm on December 14-15, 1970, according to Kosmos-381 Satellite (1974) Issled. Geomagnet. Aeronom. Fiz. Solntsa, (32), pp. 158-161; Avakyan, S.V., Vdovin, A.I., Pustarnakov, V.F., (1994) Ioniziruyushchie I Pronikayushchie Izlucheniya V Okolozemnom Kosmicheskom Prostranstve. Spravochnik (Ionizing and Penetrating Radiation in the Near-Earth Space: A Reference Book), , St. Petersburg: Gidrometeoizdat; Avakyan, S.V., Voronin, N.A., Serova, A.E., The Role of Rydberg Atoms and Molecules in the Upper Atmosphere (1997) Geomagn. Aeron., 37 (3), pp. 331-335; Bates, D.R., Electronion Recombination in an Ambient Molecular Gas (1981) J. Phys. B, 14 (18), pp. 3525-3534; Benestad, R.E., (2002) Solar Activity and Earth's Climate, p. 287. , Springer-Praxis; (2002) Bezopasnost' Rossii. Bezopasnost' Truboprovodnogo Transporta (Russia's Security. Pipeline Transportation Security), , I. I. Mazur and O. M. Ivantsov (Eds.), Moscow: MGF Znanie; Bondur, V.G., Pulinets, S.A., Kim, G.A., Role of Variations in Galactic Cosmic Rays in Tropical Cyclogenesis: Evidenc